# Cloudflare Pages _redirects
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
#
# Usage:
#   - Attach facelessanimalstudios.com as your primary custom domain
#   - Attach djfacelessanimal.com as a second custom domain on the same project
#   - Cloudflare Pages will apply these rules automatically at the edge
#
# Format: <source> <destination> <status>
# 200 = rewrite (SPA-style, URL stays the same)
# 301 = permanent redirect

# ── DYNAMIC PAGE ROUTES (SPA rewrite — URL preserved) ──────────────
# These serve the correct template HTML while keeping the clean URL.
# The page-renderer.js script reads the slug from window.location.pathname
# and fetches data from Supabase to hydrate the page.

/artist/*    /templates/artist.html    200
/creator/*   /templates/creator.html   200
/business/*  /templates/business.html  200

